
@startuml activity_create_property
title Activity Diagram â€“ Create New Property

|Property Owner|
start
:Start the procedure to create a new property;
:Enter property details (name, address, description, amenities, etc.);
:Confirm the entered data;

|System|
:Validate property data;
if (Data valid?) then (Yes)
  :Create the new property in the system;
else (No)
  :Show error message;
  stop
endif

|Property Owner|
:Decide whether to add rooms to the property;

if (Add rooms?) then (Yes)
  repeat
    :Enter room details (type, price, capacity, amenities, availability);
    |System|
    :Create a new room associated with the property;
  repeat while (Add more rooms?)
endif

|Property Owner|
:Decide whether to upload media (photos, videos);

if (Upload media?) then (Yes)
  repeat
    :Select media file;
    |System|
    :Upload and associate media with the property;
  repeat while (Upload more media?)
endif

|System|
:Confirm creation of the complete property;

|Property Owner|
:View the new property in their property list;
stop
@enduml